articles.title: Portland E-Prix: Dennis takes championship lead with pole - Motorsport.com
articles.description: Jake Dennis retook the lead of the Formula E standings by snatching his first pole position of the 2022-23 season at Portland, defeating Sacha Fenestraz in the final.
articles.content:
On his team's home turf, Andretti driver Dennis produced a lap of 1m08.931s in the pole shootout to beat Nissan rival Fenestraz by a scant 0.079s.
